{"tid":1473034,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】【緊急】機管局同民航處帶頭呃旅客，疑有陷害示威者之嫌整合post","createTime":"2019-08-14T17:38:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T16:43:58.000Z","uid":14361,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"44fe266f19f4cac07f2905314bc3a750d5223824","tid":1473034,"uid":14361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:38:00.000Z","msg":"係琴日下午4點半<span style=\"color: red;\">機管局宣佈暫停所有航班登機服務</span>，有大量航班都因為咁<span style=\"color: red;\">被機管局「取消」</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CaK6nYh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCaK6nYh.jpg&h=28fc8f68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yaoOBe8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyaoOBe8.jpg&h=0707bee8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fCxvPBJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfCxvPBJ.jpg&h=e41a9174&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但離奇嘅事係警察入嚟護送個公安就嗰陣就完全唔同咗啦，當時離境大堂十分混亂啦，所以原本塞咗嘅離境位置開通翻，之後顯示屏嘅航班情況突然<span style=\"color: red;\">由取消轉為boarding soon</span><br />\n另外小弟亦翻查咗一架航班係原定係琴晚2145起飛嘅HX761<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YrRsSra.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYrRsSra.jpg&h=21fccf96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本身應該係取消咗嫁啦但係FlightStatus呢個網站搵到佢係2343起返飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5WzumjX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5WzumjX.png&h=59305c9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">假設一個旅客見到個要搭嘅飛機顯示cancel，正常都會理解做自己班機已經被取消，但最後飛機又照飛喎咁姐係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">航空公司當佢係No Show</span>啦，亦姐係旅客就唔會claim到保險</span>，搞到係旅客自己問題。咁嘅話<span style=\"color: red;\">旅客就會怪在場嘅義士係令到佢哋搭唔到飛機嘅兇手</span>而唔係機管局同民航處。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n機管局同民航處落得呢個決定好明顯就係因為<span style=\"color: red;\">政治因素</span>，作為一個排名極高嘅國際機場竟然解決唔到示威問題就<span style=\"color: red;\">犧牲旅客嘅利益</span>。<br />\n其實機場不嬲都係香港嘅經濟命脈之一，如果呢單嘢屬實我諗<span style=\"color: red;\">機場嘅聲譽一定跌</span>因為係一個嚴重嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">醜聞</span>，到期時其他國家尤其歐美必定會譴責，而<span style=\"color: red;\">香港嘅聲譽自然亦會跌跟住就成功攬炒！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上為小弟愚見，希望大家可以集思廣益一齊傾下<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"fd4d1a9f1360d0494ccd6b9a99bd8cad8c760dc3","tid":1473034,"uid":14361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:39:32.000Z","msg":"順帶一提，呢單嘢蘋果都有報<br />\n<br />\n【逆權運動】被「取消」航班偷偷復飛 旅客空姐齊轟機管局鬼祟<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190814&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59929944\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190814%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59929944&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg25ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=016cf0db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190814%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59929944&h=4921eeb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190814&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59929944</a>"},{"pid":"3ad843a8259b55aa489e1b434f8b0df280eea216","tid":1473034,"uid":306008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:39:37.000Z","msg":"機管局好有問題<br />\n一定要出黎解釋"},{"pid":"d9522008e64b756bb8a7cb641c29077b2d2d14f2","tid":1473034,"uid":306008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:39:58.000Z","msg":"同埋要搵到受害者"},{"pid":"d58aa99a673e76aaa9d54145a6937cce9a511c12","tid":1473034,"uid":306008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:40:09.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"cbd3678e402488ae78dbae5e1f6a44577c04b26b","tid":1473034,"uid":306008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:40:27.000Z","msg":"推爆佢老味"},{"pid":"9c963d6538650f13017b711c624305350e7a13e6","tid"